      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Of the barley of the annona of the 5th epigraphe, of the horiodeiktia of Karanis, through Pan(  ), boundary inspector, eleven artabai, equal 11 artabai of barley. I, Herodes, have signed. In the 12th, 11th and 4th year, on Hathyr 1.</ab>
